{"tid":852203,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"林鄭月娥拒絕回應馬凱遭拒繼簽證事件","createTime":"2018-10-07T16:15:38.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-08T00:15:32.000Z","uid":41404,"like":2,"dislike":54,"uniUserReply":30,"replies":[{"pid":"d58b3687e2bc8200f93b35b09913b6119dc3721a","tid":852203,"uid":41404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-07T16:15:38.000Z","msg":"【Now新聞台】外國記者會第一副主席馬凱被特區政府拒續工作簽證，行政長官林鄭月娥出席活動後未有回應。外交部表明堅決支持決定，又指別國無權干涉。而《環球時報》就發表社評指香港少一名英國記者言論自由不會受損，馬凱應反思自己做過甚麼。<br />\n<br />\n馬凱8月時曾主持香港民族黨召集人陳浩天在外國記者會的午餐演講，他最近遭入境處拒絕續批工作簽證。本台向馬凱查詢會否提上訴，他透過短訊回覆指沒有新回應。<br />\n<br />\n行政長官林鄭月娥晚上出席活後，未有回應事件。馬凱可於14天內向政務司司長提出上訴，並交行政長官及行政會議考慮，張建宗亦未有回應。<br />\n<br />\n英美對事件表達關注。外交部表明，堅決支持特區政府的決定，別國無權干涉。"},{"pid":"c55bd378502c1ea3cdf705c2cb965da2ea59dc4a","tid":852203,"uid":67655,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-07T16:18:36.000Z","msg":"口硬係無用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"77649f44cc167fa11b210f0974ffcd57b399aed6","tid":852203,"uid":11148,"like":67,"dislike":0,"score":67,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-07T16:21:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/MmpxjJe.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMmpxjJe.jpg&h=9ffb08ef&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n支那自己干涉外國但就話外國無權干涉<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"df6be964aad06a8a8e7098afb1f1527a69361fe3","tid":852203,"uid":41818,"like":24,"dislike":0,"score":24,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-07T16:26:36.000Z","msg":"今次個個唔敢應<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9277bfcadc3c0edcd9a807af28da3832e70102e4","tid":852203,"uid":50457,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-07T16:27:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\